Walang idinagdag.

00:31:47.160 --> 00:31:47.960
Bilisan mo, bilisan mo!

00:31:48.240 --> 00:31:49.030
Nagugutom na ako!

00:32:08.640 --> 00:32:09.350
Mag-enjoy po kayo, ginoo.

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:44.400
Waiter!

00:32:46.400 --> 00:32:47.260
Pakitingnan naman!

